                  Angelos Stavrou and
                  Cas Cremers and
                  Elaine Shi},
	title = {Poster: ReMouse Dataset: Measuring Similarity of Human-Generated Trajectories
                  as an Important Step in Dealing with Session-Replay Bots},
	booktitle = {Proceedings of the 2022 {ACM} {SIGSAC} Conference on Computer and
                  Communications Security, {CCS} 2022, Los Angeles, CA, USA, November
                  7-11, 2022},
	pages = {3447--3449},
